---
import SiteLayout from "../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
---

<SiteLayout title="Criminal & Traffic | ImmediateLawyerHelp.com">
  <!-- Paste the page body for Criminal & Traffic here (everything between header and footer) -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="card">
        <h1>Criminal & Traffic</h1>
        <p class="muted">Paste your existing Criminal & Traffic content here.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
   <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="heroBg" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="container heroInner">
      <div class="heroCard">
        <h1>Criminal &amp; Traffic</h1>
        <p class="heroSub">
          Criminal charges and traffic matters can move quickly and carry lasting consequences.
          Choose a topic below, or describe what happened to continue.
        </p>

        <form id="heroSearchForm" class="heroSearch" autocomplete="off">
          <input
            id="issueInput"
            type="text"
            placeholder="Briefly describe what happened…"
            aria-label="Describe what happened"
          />
          <button type="submit">Get Started</button>
        </form>

        <div class="heroBadges">
          <span>Time-sensitive</span><span class="sep">•</span>
          <span>Confidential</span><span class="sep">•</span>
          <span>Independent attorneys</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Article -->
  <section class="section sectionTight">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="card">
        <article class="ctArticle">
          <h2 class="cardTitle">Common criminal and traffic cases</h2>
          <p class="muted" style="margin-top:10px; line-height:1.65; max-width:78ch;">
            These situations often involve deadlines, court dates, and paperwork that varies by state.
            The sections below provide a quick overview and link to dedicated pages (coming soon).
          </p>

          <section class="ctSection" id="criminal-defense">
            <h3 class="ctH"><a class="ctTitleLink" href="/criminal-traffic/criminal-defense/">Criminal Defense</a></h3>
            <div class="ctImage">
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1453945619913-79ec89a82c51?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=60" alt="" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
            <p class="guideMeta ctBlurb">
              Criminal defense covers a wide range of charges, from misdemeanors to serious felonies.
              These cases can involve arrest procedures, bail, court appearances, and evidence review.
              Early legal guidance can help clarify options, obligations, and what happens next.
            </p>
            <a class="ctLearn" href="/criminal-traffic/criminal-defense/">Learn more →</a>
          </section>

          <section class="ctSection" id="dui-dwi-drug">
            <h3 class="ctH"><a class="ctTitleLink" href="/criminal-traffic/dui-dwi-drug-charges/">DUI / DWI / Drug Charges</a></h3>
            <div class="ctImage">
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1521199646462-4e3d6f1f213e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=60" alt="" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
            <p class="guideMeta ctBlurb">
              DUI, DWI, and drug-related charges can affect driving privileges, employment, and criminal records.
              These cases often involve traffic stops, field tests, breath or blood testing, and strict response timelines.
              Missing a deadline can increase penalties or limit available options.
            </p>
            <a class="ctLearn" href="/criminal-traffic/dui-dwi-drug-charges/">Learn more →</a>
          </section>

          <section class="ctSection" id="traffic-tickets">
            <h3 class="ctH"><a class="ctTitleLink" href="/criminal-traffic/traffic-tickets/">Traffic Tickets</a></h3>
            <div class="ctImage">
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1483729558449-99ef09a8c325?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=60" alt="" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
            <p class="guideMeta ctBlurb">
              Traffic violations can include speeding, reckless driving, license issues, or failure to appear.
              Even routine tickets may lead to fines, points, higher insurance costs, or license consequences.
              Some citations may be contestable depending on the facts and local rules.
            </p>
            <a class="ctLearn" href="/criminal-traffic/traffic-tickets/">Learn more →</a>
          </section>

          <section class="ctSection" id="domestic-violence-assault">
            <h3 class="ctH"><a class="ctTitleLink" href="/criminal-traffic/domestic-violence-assault/">Domestic Violence / Assault</a></h3>
            <div class="ctImage">
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1526374965328-7f61d4dc18c5?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=60" alt="" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
            <p class="guideMeta ctBlurb">
              Domestic violence and assault allegations often involve protective orders, court restrictions, and criminal exposure.
              These situations can be urgent and may affect housing, contact with family, and future court outcomes.
              Understanding immediate obligations and the process early can reduce uncertainty.
            </p>
            <a class="ctLearn" href="/criminal-traffic/domestic-violence-assault/">Learn more →</a>
          </section>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Keep sideSearchForm present (homepage scripts may attach listeners) -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container twoCol">
      <div class="card">
        <h2 class="cardTitle">Not sure which applies?</h2>
        <p class="muted" style="line-height:1.6; max-width:72ch;">
          Describe what happened and we’ll route you to the right next step.
        </p>

        <form id="sideSearchForm" class="sideSearch" autocomplete="off">
          <input type="text" placeholder="Describe your issue…" aria-label="Describe your issue" />
          <button type="submit" aria-label="Search">→</button>
        </form>
      </div>

      <aside class="card">
        <h2 class="cardTitle">Notes</h2>
        <ul class="bullets">
          <li>Information on this site is not legal advice.</li>
          <li>Using this site does not create an attorney-client relationship.</li>
          <li>Independent attorneys may have different availability and policies.</li>
        </ul>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    /* Criminal/Traffic page-specific styling: restrained images, article rhythm */
    .ctArticle .ctSection{
      padding: 18px 0 34px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
    }
    .ctArticle .ctSection:last-of-type{
      border-bottom: 0;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .ctH{
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 18px;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }
    .ctTitleLink{
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .ctTitleLink:hover{
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .ctImage{
      margin: 12px 0 18px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      overflow: hidden;
      max-width: 62%;
    }
    .ctImage img{
      width: 100%;
      height: 140px;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
      filter: saturate(.9) contrast(.95);
    }
    @media (max-width: 900px){
      .ctImage{ max-width: 100%; }
    }
    .ctBlurb{
      margin-top: 10px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      max-width: 78ch;
    }
    .ctLearn{
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-top: 12px;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 650;
    }
    .ctLearn:hover{
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.06);
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,.14);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</SiteLayout>
